stupid question: what is a blob page?
It's a page that represents an individual blob in a repository.  Usually that means a specific file at a specific revision.  E.g. https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/master/actionmailer/CHANGELOG
You can also hit "t" in any repo to get a list of files and start typing names to filter down. Good stuff
Or press ? for a list of everything :)
